posts.description:
An ode to heart feels.

Happy Valentine's Day, lovers. xS

#Valentinesday #love #rumi

TRULY YOURS.

Today while celebrating the insanely stunning land we get to call home - Terra Australis - let's not forget to show our respect to our indigenous brothers and sisters; the beautiful people who have called this sunburnt island home for 60,000 years longer than anyone else.

The heart of this land beats in time with yours, truly.

#Australia #TerraAustralis

PS. There's a special coloured version on my Insta story  for those that want to repost a colourful tribute üñ§üíõ‚ù§Ô∏è EDIT: just realised it's not the best quality. If you want a better quality version DM me and I'll send to you x

At the end of the day (or year)... regardless of ups and downs that make us wish the day (or year) away, the vast majority of us reading this really are incredibly lucky to be living in paradise.
Everyday we have the opportunity to start fresh and strive for greatness... so as refreshing as a new year can feel, please don't ever wish your year away in order to start fresh. See everyday as a new beginning.
Wishing you love and greatness this year, today and everyday.
Happy New Year!
xS
#2017

5 years old, doing ballet around the Hills Hoist in my Bensville backyard to the demo song on my keyboard because I wasn't allowed to do real ballet classes.
My first memory of George Michael.
Thanks for the magic, dear George. My ballet dreams/memories will always be connected to you.
#RIPGeorgeMichael #Jitterbug #GeorgeMichael #Wham #2016enoughalready

xS
